data.text:
Career: 2019 CSCAA Honorable Mention Scholar All-American ... 2019 All-Patriot League Second Team ... scored 105 points at the Patriot League Championships ... one-time Patriot League individual medalist, winning silver in the 100 breaststroke in 2019 ... graduated with school records in the 100 breaststroke (54.12) and 200 breaststroke (1:58.85) ... first Bison to clear 55 seconds in the 100 breaststroke ... second Bison to clear 2:00 in the 200 breaststroke ... member of nine relays with program top-10 times, including the record-holding 200 medley relay (1:29.19), 400 medley relay (3:16.51) and 200 freestyle relay (1:20.82) teams ... one-time Patriot League Swimmer of the Week ... 12 first-place finishes in individual events.

2018-19 (Senior): CSCAA Honorable Mention Scholar All-American ... earned spot on the All-Patriot League Second Team after finishing second among Bison with 29 points at the Patriot League Championships ... captured a silver medal in the 100 breaststroke by clocking a school-record time of 54.12 ... became the first Bison to clear 55 seconds in that event ... was a member of the bronze medalist 200 medley and 400 medley relay teams ... also took seventh in the 200 breaststroke and helped the 200 freestyle relay team place fourth ... in the preliminaries of the 200 breaststroke, broke school standard with a time of 1:58.85 ... became the second Bison to clear 2:00 in that event ... the 200 medley (1:29.19) and 200 freestyle (1:20.82) clocked school-record times ... at the ECAC Championships, took 16th in the 100 butterfly and was a member of the third-place 400 medley and fourth-place 200 medley relay teams ... at the Bucknell Invitational, placed second in the 200 breaststroke and third in the 100 breaststroke ... was also a member of the second-place 200 medley relay, fourth-place 400 medley and fourth-place 200 freestyle teams ... won seven individual events over the course of the season, tied with Matt McGoey for the most of any swimmer ... presented Bucknell's Lee S. "Bud" Ranck Memorial Award for outstanding spirit and contributions to the Bucknell athletic program ... member of Patriot League Academic Honor Roll.

2017-18 (Junior): Scored 27 points at the Patriot League Championships with a fifth-place finish in the 200 breaststroke and a sixth-place showing in the 100 breaststroke ... posted team season-best time in the 100 breaststroke finals (54.97) and 200 breaststroke finals (2:00.25) ... member of bronze medalist 400 medley relay team that clocked school record time of 3:16.51 ... member of bronze medalist 200 medley relay team, which recorded the second-fastest time (1:29.78) in school history ... also placed 25th in the preliminaries of the 200 IM ... won the 100 breaststroke and 200 breaststroke in dual against Lehigh ... finished fourth in the 200 breaststroke, seventh in the 100 breaststroke and eighth in the 100 butterfly at the Bucknell Invite ... member of 200 medley relay team that took sixth at the ECAC Championships ... also placed 23rd in the preliminaries of the 100 butterfly ... represented Bucknell at the USA Winter Nationals, tying for 35th in the 100 breaststroke and taking 37th in the 200 breaststroke ... member of Patriot League Academic Honor Roll.

2016-17 (Sophomore): Scored 28 points at the Patriot League Championships with fifth-place finishes in the 100 breaststroke and 200 breaststroke ... also took 19th in the 200 IM and swam on the second-place 200 medley relay and fourth-place 400 medley relay ... scored one point at the ECAC Championships with a 16th-place finish in the 100 breaststroke ... competed in seven events during the season (100 free, 500 free, 50 breaststroke, 100 breaststroke, 200 breaststroke, 200 IM, 100 fly) ... 11 top-three finishes in individual events ... won the 100 breaststroke against UMBC, Loyola, and Lehigh ... named the Patriot League Swimmer of the Week (10/4) after the meet against UMBC.

2015-16 (Freshman): Scored 21 points at the Patriot League Championships, finishing seventh in the 100 breaststroke and ninth in the 200 breaststroke with season-best times ... added a 21st-place finish in the 200 IM and swam a leg on the 400 medley relay that took fifth ... competed at the ECAC Championships, where he took 19th in the 200 breaststroke, 28th in the 100 breaststroke and 52nd in the 100 fly ... took sixth as part of the 400 medley relay at the ECAC meet ... competed in five different events during the season (50 free, 100 breaststroke, 200 breaststroke, 200 IM, 100 fly) ... had four top-three finishes in the 100 breaststroke and four top-five finishes in the 200 breaststroke ... member of Patriot League Academic Honor Roll.
